\c 15
\s Umnyaka wokuyekela imilandu
\p
\v 1 Ekupheleni kweminyaka yonke eyisikhombisa uzakwenza inkululeko\x + 14.9; 31.10; 14.12. Eks. 23.10,11. Levi 25.2-4.\x*.
\v 2 Njalo le yindlela yenkululeko: Wonke umkweledisi oweboleka umakhelwane wakhe uzakhulula \add isikwelede\add*; kayiku\add si\add*bamba ngamandla kumakhelwane wakhe kumbe kumfowabo, ngoba kumenyezelwe inkululeko eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 3 Kowezizweni uza\add si\add*bamba ngamandla; kodwa lokho okwakho okukumfowenu isandla sakho sizakukhulula\x + 23.20.\x*;
\v 4 ukuze kungabi lomyanga phakathi kwakho; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* izakubusisa lokukubusisa elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona ukuthi libe yilifa ukudla ilifa lalo\x + 28.8.\x*,
\v 5 kuphela uba ulalela lokulalela ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ugcine ukuyenza limithetho yonke engikulaya yona lamuhla\x + 28.1.\x*.
\v 6 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izakubusisa njengokuthembisa kwayo kuwe. Njalo uzakweboleka izizwe ezinengi, kodwa wena kawuyikweboleka \add kuzo\x + 28.12,44.\x*\add*; uzabusa izizwe ezinengi, kodwa wena kaziyikukubusa\x + 28.13; Zaga 22.7.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Uba kukhona phakathi kwakho umyanga ongomunye wabafowenu, kwelinye lamasango akho, elizweni lakho, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika lona, ungenzi lukhuni inhliziyo yakho, ungamvaleli umfowenu ongumyanga isandla sakho\x + 2.30; 1 Joha. 3.17.\x*,
\v 8 kodwa uzamvulela lokumvulela isandla sakho, umeboleke lokumeboleka okwanela ukuswela kwakhe, lokho akuswelayo\x + Levi 25.35. Mat. 5.42. Luka 6.34,35.\x*.
\v 9 Ziqaphele hlezi kube khona ilizwi enhliziyweni yakho embi lisithi: Umnyaka wesikhombisa, umnyaka wenkululeko useduze; lelihlo lakho libe libi limelane lomfowenu ongumyanga, ukuze ungamniki\x + 28.54,56. Zaga 23.6.; 28.22. Mat. 20.15.\x*, abesekhala ngawe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 24.15.\x*, njalo kube yisono kuwe\x + Mat. 25.41,42.\x*.
\v 10 Umnike lokumnika, lenhliziyo yakho ingadani nxa umnika\x + 2 Kor. 9.7.\x*; ngoba ngenxa yalinto iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izakubusisa emsebenzini wonke wakho\x + 14.29.\x* lakukho konke obeka kukho isandla sakho\x + 12.7.\x*.
\v 11 Ngoba umyanga kayikuphela phakathi kwelizwe\x + Mat. 26.11. Mark. 14.7. Joha. 12.8.\x*. Ngakho ngiyakulaya ngithi: Uzamvulela kakhulu isandla sakho umfowenu, umyanga wakho, loswelayo wakho, elizweni lakho\x + 15.8.\x*.
\s Ukuphathwa kwezigqili
\p
\v 12 Uba umfowenu, umHebheru loba umHebherukazi, ethengiswa kuwe, akusebenzele iminyaka eyisithupha, ngakho ngomnyaka wesikhombisa uzamyekela ukuthi ahambe ekhululekile asuke kuwe\x + Eks. 21.2. Jer. 34.14. Levi 25.39-41.\x*.
\v 13 Lalapho umyekela ukuthi ahambe ekhululekile esuka kuwe, ungamyekeli ukuthi ahambe engaphathanga lutho;
\v 14 uzamnakekela lokumnakekela ezimvini zakho, lokwebala lokubhulela lakho, lokwesikhamelo sakho sewayini; \add ku\add*lokho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekubusise ngakho uzamupha\x + 8.18.\x*.
\v 15 Njalo uzakhumbula ukuthi wawuyisigqili elizweni leGibhithe, lokuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho yakuhlenga. Ngalokho ngiyakulaya linto lamuhla\x + 5.15.\x*.
\v 16 Kodwa kuzakuthi, uba esithi kuwe: Kangiyikusuka kuwe, ngoba ethanda wena lendlu yakho, ngoba kulungile kuye elawe\x + Eks. 21.5,6.\x*,
\v 17 uzathatha usungulo, ubhobozele indlebe yakhe \add ngalo\add* esivalweni, ukuze abe yisigqili sakho laphakade. Lakuso isigqilikazi sakho wenze njalo.
\v 18 Kakungabi lukhuni emehlweni akho nxa umyekela ehamba ekhululekile kuwe; ngoba ngokuphindwe kabili kweholo lesiqatshwa ukusebenzele iminyaka eyisithupha. Ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izakubusisa kukho konke okwenzayo\x + Isa. 16.14. 21.16.\x*.
\s Amazibulo ezifuyo
\p
\v 19 Wonke amazibulo azazalwa enkomeni zakho lezimvini zakho, amaduna, uzawangcwelisela iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + Eks. 13.2.\x*; kawuyikusebenza ngezibulo lejongosi lakho, futhi kawuyikugunda izibulo lezimvu zakho\x + Levi 25.39.\x*.
\v 20 Phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho uzalidla, umnyaka ngomnyaka, endaweni iN\nd kosi\nd* ezayikhetha, wena lendlu yakho\x + 12.5,6.\x*.
\v 21 Kodwa uba kulesici kulo, liqhula, loba liyisiphofu, loba lilasiphi isici esibi, ungalihlabeli iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + Levi 22.20.\x*.
\v 22 Uzalidla phakathi kwamasango akho, ongahlambulukanga lohlambulukileyo \add bazalidla\add* bendawonye, njengomziki lanjengendluzele\x + 12.15.\x*.
\v 23 Kuphela igazi lalo ungalidli; ulichithele emhlabathini njengamanzi\x + Levi 3.17.\x*.